These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, card-games, chineseing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, vegafina, ritmeester, montecristo
4 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, canasta, backgammon
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, chinese, nigerian, indonesian
1. the vegafina-smoker is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the person playing canasta is the havana-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is chineseing is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
7. the vegafina-smoker is the indian##1
8. the person playing snooker is on the right of the nigerian##1
9. the person who's hobby is chineseing is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | board-games  | chineseing  | camping | card-games |
| Cigar           | vegafina | havana | montecristo  | ritmeester  |
| Game   | backgammon       | canasta      | monopoly | snooker      |
| Nationality           | indian          | chinese     | nigerian    | indonesian     |

