.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, sprite, tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, january, november, february
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, russian, polish, british
4 different pets are kept: mouse, pony, hedgehog, horse
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
2. the british is the owner of the mouse##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the british is on the left of the brazilian##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the polish##1
7. the russian is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
9. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | cola       | iced-tea | tea        |
| Birthday          | february     | january       | november   | april   |
| Nationality   | polish      | russian       | british     | brazilian    |
| Pet         | hedgehog | horse | mouse | pony |

