.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, july, september, november
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, taxi, trike, skateboard
There 4 different types of food: avocado, pineapple, watermelon, raspberry
 1. the person drinking tea is the person eating raspberry##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 3. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up       | tea        | mirinda        |
| Birthday           | july   | september | december   | november |
| Transport   | motorbike     | taxi    | skateboard | trike        |
| Food           | watermelon         | avocado  | raspberry       | pineapple         |

