2. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
6. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who growslily##1
7. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
8. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far right##1
9. the person playing backgammon is the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Flower           | lily   | poppy  | rose | iris |
