.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
4 different games are played: snooker, canasta, backgammon, domino
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, orange, brown, azure
There are 4 different nationalities: french, indian, thai, turkish
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, banana, pumpkin, kiwi
1. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1
2. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person eating banana is on the far left##1
4. the indian is on the left of the french##1
5. the turkish is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
6. the person eating kiwi is the thai##1
7. the french is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
8. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
9. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Game           | snooker  | backgammon    | canasta | domino |
| Color   | brown      | orange    | grey         | azure    |
| Nationality   | indian   | french     | thai          | turkish      |
| Food         | banana | watermelon | kiwi      | pumpkin      |

