 2. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person playing billiard##1
 3. the person who growslily is the person playing poker##1
 4. the owner of the horse is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 5. the person playing bridge is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 6. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| City          | edinburgh  | rome | venice     | hamburg |
| Flower           | zinnia  | daffodil      | lily | sunflower    |
| Game   | billiard | bridge  | poker    | chess  |
| Pet           | horse   | mouse       | fish       | frog      |

