 3. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the police-officer is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the coach##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the dressmaker is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 8. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
 9. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
10. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre    | funk | reggae     | punk    | d&b |
